      <title>Known MacroQuest Hacker active on Bertoxx</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Bertoxxulous&amp;message.id=179#M179</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;The following details the actions of a known MQ type Hacker active on our server and the details surrounding how I came to know about him&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Hackers Name: Cyendia (Unguilded)&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Class : Rogue&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Level: 69&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Race dark Elf.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Last Year in later part of 2005, Myself and 3 friends were doing Nameds in RCOD. We were there for several hours in total and during that time afair, only 1 other person was ever in zone, Cyendia. Now we were doing our thing killing mobs and doing what we all regularly do, when at one point, wel all begain to receive DUEL requests seemingly from each other. Now as we were in battle I just assumed the guys were jokeing around and didnt think much of it at that moment. We moved to our next spot and were killing a kyv, when suddenly I began to take damage from a 'Cyendia'. I could not See anyone or anything attacking me and eventually I was killed.&amp;nbsp; After i was resed back(none of my friends were killed.) Not sure if its the nature of the hack he used that only I was open to attack or perhaps he just felt killing an entire party was something even Sony wouldnt ignore. In any event when confronted by all of us, he lauched into various tirades to&amp;nbsp;each of us&amp;nbsp;about how we were cheaters ourselves and and various insults and frabricated events that simply didnt accord with reality. &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Why were we attacked at all? MQ hackers usually dont like to draw too much attention to themselves but reflecting on the event afterwards, its quite obvious we were simply interfering with his activities in RCOD and we were in his way. So , he decided to run us off or teach us a lesson.&amp;nbsp; After that specific incident the Cyendia character kept a decidely low profile and only appeared very few times. after that.&amp;nbsp;Only once or twice for very short time spans and none that we are aware of latetly. That however has now changed and this &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Hacker is back on Bertoxx and has been for several days now for extended periods of time. He hangs out primarily in WOS and I have noted for a rogue he seems to OOC the locations and spawns of the nameds there. Seems hes either in the right place at always the right time or...(cough cough).&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;That is all the information I have on this Known Hacker. This is not one of these. I let out my password and usernamedand now Im broke&amp;amp;naked in bazzar. He will actively attack and kill players with bogus duel requests (his last known method, i dont doubt there are other means available&amp;nbsp;to MQ cheaters.) Its more than likely he has the ability to solo and kill Mobs, named or otherwise,&amp;nbsp;with no chance for them to retaliate. This would make sense as i was attacked in a manner where i could not&amp;nbsp;see and target anything, yet was killed just the same. Its no stretch to assume he farmed many named in this same manner. So Bertoxx, be aware of this person and please if see him about and notice anything unusal at all about him, dont hesitate to report him imediately. If you see him in zone, please let it be known who and what he is. I know SoE take a real soft line when it comes to hackers but, if you care at all, at least we can inform each other the best we can. You woudl think that attacking and killing legimate players would a least get SoE off the couch once in a while, but that does not seem to be the case. I do not doubt for one second he has a full set of alts on that account. So yes, it probable hes continued his activities steady since then, but its only recently he has been logging in as Cyendia again.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Thanks everyone&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
