&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;We raid in EST prime time.&amp;nbsp; Most of our raids begin at 7:00 pm EST and run for a few hours.&amp;nbsp; On Saturdays, we like to start earlier, around 5:00pm EST.&amp;nbsp; We raid 5 days a week, our days off are Friday and Sunday, though that is subject to change in the future.&amp;nbsp; We use a Tiered DKP system to distribute loot in our guild.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
